scoringPlays.text: Trey Ragas 11 Yd Run (Stevie Artigue Kick)
Trey Ragas 2 Yd Run (Stevie Artigue Kick)
Anthony D. Taylor 1 Yd Run (Foster Hilborn Kick)
Keenan Barnes 8 Yd pass from Andre Nunez (Stevie Artigue Kick)

videos.description: Trey Ragas runs 11 yards for a touchdown to give Louisiana an early lead over Texas State.
videos.headline: Louisiana scores first with TD

videos.description: Trey Ragas finds the end zone once again on a 2-yard run to increase Louisiana's lead.
videos.headline: Ragas has second TD of first quarter

videos.description: Willie Jones III's pass is intercepted by Louisiana's Tracy Walker and returned for 10 yards.
videos.headline: Texas State gets picked off in the end zone

videos.description: Texas State quarterback Willie Jones III goes deep to Thurman Morbley, getting the Bobcats closer to the red zone.
videos.headline: Jones is right on the money with deep pass

videos.description: The Bobcats are chipping away at the Ragin' Cajuns' lead with a 1-yard rushing touchdown by Anthony Taylor.
videos.headline: Taylor gets Texas State on the board with rushing TD

videos.description: Andre Nunez finds a wide-open Keenan Barnes for an 8-yard touchdown to increase Louisiana's lead over Texas State.
videos.headline: Louisiana pads lead with TD
